OL,3,C'Lay out a new path for Britain': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham sets out nationwide change
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has said he hopes to "lay
OL,7,Fout a new path for Britain" after his
OL,8,Fwin in Makerfield in which he says his
OL,9,Fconstituents "issued quite a clear
OL,10,Fcall for change".
OL,12,FBurnham described his win as a
OL,13,F"turning point" for the party, as he
OL,14,Ffocused on immigration,
OL,15,Freindustrialisation, and the cost of
OL,16,Fliving at an event to mark his victory.
OL,18,FHe hailed his team and praised the
OL,19,FNorth West as he spoke to a packed
OL,20,Fcrowd at Ashton Town FC in Ashton-in-
OL,21,FMakerfield.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
