OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781979086
OL,3,C'Lay out a new path for Britain': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham sets out nationwide change
OL,6,FHe said: "This campaign was won by a
OL,7,Fband of strong northern power women. I
OL,8,Fwouldn't mess with them and I suggest
OL,9,Fthat you don't either.
OL,11,F"This part of the world, the people
OL,12,Fhere, issued quite a clear call for a
OL,13,Fchange."
OL,15,FBurnham proceeded to thank "selfless"
OL,16,FLabour MP Josh Simmons, who stepped
OL,17,Fdown in order to allow the Greater
OL,18,FManchester Mayor to run for Parliament.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
