FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781979086
OL,3,C'Lay out a new path for Britain': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham sets out nationwide change
OL,6,FHe said: "Such was the power of what
OL,7,Fpeople said in early May, you realised
OL,8,Fthis wasn't business as usual.
OL,10,F"It needed a profound response, and
OL,11,Fyou did something incredibly selfless
OL,12,Fin stepping forward and working with
OL,13,Fme.
OL,15,F"It does now open the space for the
OL,16,Freal change that the people of this
OL,17,Fconstituency deserve."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
