PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781979086
OL,3,C'Lay out a new path for Britain': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham sets out nationwide change
OL,6,FBurnham has indicated he would put
OL,7,Fhimself forward in an expected
OL,8,Fchallenge to Starmer's leadership, as
OL,9,Fhe said this would be "a last chance
OL,10,Fto change."
OL,12,FHe called for an end to "trickle-down
OL,13,Feconomics", which he said "didn't
OL,14,Ftrickle down very much at all to
OL,15,Fplaces like this."
OL,17,FThe new MP said: "We need an economy
OL,18,Fthat works for people right here.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
