PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781979086
OL,3,C'Lay out a new path for Britain': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham sets out nationwide change
OL,6,F"We do need to bring down water bills,
OL,7,Fenergy bills, rail fares, just as
OL,8,Fwe've brought down bus fares in
OL,9,FGreater Manchester to make life more
OL,10,Faffordable for people."
OL,12,FBurnham said he repeatedly heard
OL,13,Fvoters voice concerns about the
OL,14,F"unfairness of the immigration system"
OL,15,Fduring the campaign.
OL,17,FHe said areas were becoming "HMO
OL,18,FBritain", referring to the practice of
OL,19,Fhousing asylum seekers in houses of
OL,20,Fmultiple occupation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
