PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781979086
OL,3,C'Lay out a new path for Britain': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham sets out nationwide change
OL,6,FHe said: "It's not fair that they
OL,7,Fthink that they can just operate like
OL,8,Fthat and not hear the call of people
OL,9,Fhere, the decent people here, who
OL,10,Falways will do the right thing, the
OL,11,Fcompassionate thing, but not when it's
OL,12,Funfair in terms of the way places like
OL,13,Fthis are treated."
OL,15,FThe former Greater Manchester Mayor
OL,16,Freiterated his call to revive industry
OL,17,Facross the country.
OL,26,@uD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
