OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781979086
OL,3,C'Lay out a new path for Britain': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham sets out nationwide change
OL,6,FHe said: "We want to see a new drive
OL,7,Fof reindustrialisation across the
OL,8,Fnorth of England, and indeed the rest
OL,9,Fof the country.
OL,11,F"It's about time we started backing
OL,12,FBritish business and British industry,
OL,13,Fso that we can reindustrialise places
OL,14,Flike this."
OL,16,FHe also called for education reforms
OL,17,Fto open up pathways into industry for
OL,18,Fyoung people.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
