OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781979086
OL,3,C'Lay out a new path for Britain': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham sets out nationwide change
OL,6,F"No more an education system dominated
OL,7,Fby the university route, but an
OL,8,Feducation system that offers a path
OL,9,Ffor everybody, academic and technical,
OL,10,Fin equal balance.
OL,12,F"There was a risk that would carry on
OL,13,Fseeing Britain and the politics of our
OL,14,Fcountry go down a path towards greater
OL,15,Fdarkness and division.
OL,17,F"We will not let that happen here. We
OL,18,Fwill bring people back together."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
