OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781979086
OL,3,C'Lay out a new path for Britain': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham sets out nationwide change
OL,6,FHe continued: "We will take the energy
OL,7,Fof this campaign and we will bring it
OL,8,Fforward into changing British politics
OL,9,Ffor the better, and to make this part
OL,10,Fof the world ` if you like Makerfield
OL,11,Ftest ` at the heart of British
OL,12,Fpolitics.
OL,14,F"When policies come forward, if they
OL,15,Fdon't work for people here, for the
OL,16,Fplaces of this constituency, if they
OL,17,Fdon't lift people up, then they
OL,18,Fshouldn't happen at all.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
